Camoflage::

She  transformed into bot mode and scooped up Elita in her arms.  She 
looked like a little girl with a large stuffed animal except the 
animal was Elita.  She wobbled them both towards the mess hall. "Hey, 
you might want something to eat huh?"  She groaned a bit since Elita 
wa heavier than she thought. She still had several hallways to go 
through be fore she would reach the mess hall.  She stopped for a bit 
and leaned against the wall while holding Elita. "Ah, well, your a 
bit bigger than I thought. However, since I have to be the big bot 
here, I'll just have to carry you since that's what big bots do for 
little bots like you. Anyway, you think of what you want and I'll get 
it for you when I get to the food counter."  She was breathing heavy 
as she waddled down the hall at a slow pace towards the mess hall.
